text: Trust Fall (Side B) is the fifth EP by rock band Incubus. It was released on April 17, 2020. It serves as a sequel to Trust Fall (Side A), which was released in 2015. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== Incubus * Brandon Boyd – lead vocals * Michael Einziger – guitars * Jose Pasillas II – drums * Chris Kilmore – piano, keyboards, turntables * Ben Kenney – bass, backing vocals ==References== Category:2020 EPs Category:Incubus (band) albums
title: Trust Fall (Side B)
